        <item>
            <title>周永恒疑踩「风火轮」被捕，涉无第三保、在行人路上驾驶</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/25/roy-chow-arrested-because-of-electric-mobility-devices/life-tech/smartcity/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=roy-chow-arrested-because-of-electric-mobility-devices</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/25/roy-chow-arrested-because-of-electric-mobility-devices/life-tech/smartcity/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 10:45:08 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[电动可移动工具]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[风火轮]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1299350</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>前艺人周永恒日前在天水围行人路上，因涉嫌违法使用电动可移动工具「风火轮」被警方拘捕。事件中，他被多名便衣警员制服并锁上手铐，其间情绪激动，大喊「救命」并要求围观者拍摄。警方最终将他带走，现场遗留一部疑似涉案的风火轮。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299351" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032535203-347x580.jpg" alt="" width="347" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032535203-347x580.jpg 347w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032535203.jpg 539w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 347px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲现场疑似涉案的「风火轮」</p><p>当日下午警方在天水围区内巡逻发现周永恒在行人路上俗称「风火轮」的电动可移动工具。据报警方以涉嫌「没有第三者保险而使用汽车」及「在行人路上驾驶」两项罪名将他拘捕。他在被制服时激烈反抗，多次高呼「我无撞到人呀」，场面一度混乱。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299353" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032534934-405x580.jpg" alt="" width="405" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032534934-405x580.jpg 405w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032534934.jpg 628w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 405px" /></p><p>网上流传的影片显示，数名便衣警员将他按在地上，有人以膝盖压住其腿部，另有警员递上手铐。军装警员其后到场协助，周永恒最终被带返天水围警署调查。目前他已获准保释候查，须于 5 月中旬向警方报到。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299356" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032534914-352x580.jpg" alt="" width="352" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032534914-352x580.jpg 352w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032534914.jpg 546w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 352px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲现场疑似涉案的「风火轮」</p><p>近年香港政府非常关注电动可移动工具（如风火轮）。运输署资料显示，在行车道、行人路及单车径上使用「电动可移动工具」（例如：电动滑板车、电动单轮车、电动平衡车、电动滑板、电动单车等）可能违反《道路交通条例》（香港法例第 374 章）及其附属法例，以及其他相关法例。警方近年加强执法，尤其针对在行人路上非法使用电动可移动工具行为。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%91%A8%E6%B0%B8%E6%81%86%E5%A4%A9%E6%B0%B4%E5%9C%8D%E7%96%91%E9%81%95%E6%B3%95%E8%B8%A9%E3%80%8C%E9%A2%A8%E7%81%AB%E8%BC%AA%E3%80%8D%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E9%81%AD-4-%E8%AD%A6%E6%8C%89%E5%9C%B0%E9%8E%96%E6%89%8B%E9%8A%AC%E7%8B%82%E5%8F%AB%E6%95%91%E5%91%BD-135450846.html">Yahoo</a>、<a href="https://www.td.gov.hk/tc/road_safety/electric_mobility_devices/index.html">运输署</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/03/25/roy-chow-arrested-because-of-electric-mobility-devices/life-tech/smartcity/">周永恒疑踩「风火轮」被捕，涉无第三保、在行人路上驾驶</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/25/roy-chow-arrested-because-of-electric-mobility-devices/life-tech/smartcity/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
